---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">

<head>

    <title>
        About Us | Passport Eligibility Checker
    </title>

    <meta
        name="description"
        content="Learn more about Passport Eligibility Checker, our mission, privacy-first approach and how we help users verify document consistency before passport applications."
    />

</head>

<body class="bg-slate-50">

    <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">

        <!-- Hero Section -->

        <section
            class="
                relative
                overflow-hidden
                py-24
                text-center
            "
        >

            <div
                class="
                    absolute
                    top-0
                    left-1/2
                    -translate-x-1/2
                    w-[500px]
                    h-[500px]
                    rounded-full
                    bg-blue-200/20
                    blur-3xl
                "
            ></div>

            <span
                class="
                    text-blue-600
                    font-semibold
                    uppercase
                    tracking-widest
                "
            >
                About Us
            </span>

            <h1
                class="
                    mt-4
                    text-5xl
                    font-bold
                    text-slate-900
                "
            >
                Helping Users Verify
                Passport Documents
                With Confidence
            </h1>

            <p
                class="
                    mt-6
                    text-xl
                    text-slate-600
                    max-w-3xl
                    mx-auto
                    leading-8
                "
            >
                Passport Eligibility Checker is an
                independent verification platform
                designed to help users review
                document consistency before
                beginning the passport application
                process.
            </p>

        </section>

        <!-- Mission -->

        <section
            class="
                bg-white
                rounded-3xl
                border
                border-slate-200
                p-10
                shadow-sm
            "
        >

            <h2
                class="
                    text-3xl
                    font-bold
                    text-slate-900
                "
            >
                Our Mission
            </h2>

            <p
                class="
                    mt-6
                    text-slate-600
                    leading-8
                "
            >
                Applying for a passport often
                requires multiple identity and
                supporting documents. Small
                inconsistencies in names, dates of
                birth or other personal information
                can create confusion during document
                review and verification.
            </p>

            <p
                class="
                    mt-4
                    text-slate-600
                    leading-8
                "
            >
                Our mission is to provide users with
                a simple and secure way to review
                document consistency before
                submitting applications. By using
                OCR technology and automated
                comparison methods, we help identify
                potential issues early so users can
                review their records with greater
                confidence.
            </p>

        </section>

        <!-- Features -->

        <section
            class="
                py-20
                grid
                md:grid-cols-2
                gap-8
            "
        >

            <div
                class="
                    bg-white
                    rounded-3xl
                    border
                    border-slate-200
                    p-8
                    shadow-sm
                "
            >

                <h3
                    class="
                        text-2xl
                        font-bold
                    "
                >
                    What We Do
                </h3>

                <ul
                    class="
                        mt-6
                        space-y-4
                        text-slate-600
                    "
                >

                    <li>
                        ✓ OCR Based Document Extraction
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        ✓ Aadhaar Information Review
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        ✓ PAN Information Review
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        ✓ Identity Consistency Checks
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        ✓ Verification Summary Reports
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        ✓ Password Protected PDF Support
                    </li>

                </ul>

            </div>

            <div
                class="
                    bg-white
                    rounded-3xl
                    border
                    border-slate-200
                    p-8
                    shadow-sm
                "
            >

                <h3
                    class="
                        text-2xl
                        font-bold
                    "
                >
                    Why Users Trust Us
                </h3>

                <ul
                    class="
                        mt-6
                        space-y-4
                        text-slate-600
                    "
                >

                    <li>
                        🔒 Privacy Focused Approach
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        ☁️ No Unnecessary Data Storage
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        🛡️ Secure Verification Workflow
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        📄 Transparent Verification Results
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        ⚡ Fast Browser-Based Processing
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        🤝 Independent Verification Tool
                    </li>

                </ul>

            </div>

        </section>

        <!-- Commitment -->

        <section
            class="
                bg-gradient-to-r
                from-blue-50
                via-white
                to-indigo-50
                rounded-3xl
                border
                border-blue-100
                p-10
            "
        >

            <h2
                class="
                    text-3xl
                    font-bold
                    text-slate-900
                "
            >
                Our Commitment To Privacy
            </h2>

            <p
                class="
                    mt-6
                    text-slate-600
                    leading-8
                "
            >
                We understand that identity
                documents contain sensitive
                information. Privacy and security
                remain important considerations
                throughout the verification process.
                Our goal is to provide a user
                experience that prioritizes
                transparency, trust and responsible
                handling of personal information.
            </p>

            <p
                class="
                    mt-4
                    text-slate-600
                    leading-8
                "
            >
                Users should always review official
                passport requirements and guidelines
                from relevant authorities before
                making application decisions.
            </p>

        </section>

        <!-- CTA -->

        <section
            class="
                py-24
                text-center
            "
        >

            <h2
                class="
                    text-4xl
                    font-bold
                    text-slate-900
                "
            >
                Ready To Verify Your Documents?
            </h2>

            <p
                class="
                    mt-4
                    text-slate-600
                    text-lg
                "
            >
                Check document consistency before
                starting your passport application.
            </p>

            <a
                href="/"
                class="
                    inline-block
                    mt-8
                    px-8
                    py-4
                    rounded-xl
                    bg-blue-600
                    text-white
                    font-semibold
                    hover:bg-blue-700
                    transition
                "
            >
                Start Verification
            </a>

        </section>

    </main>

</body>

</html>